    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>coriander </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Top, tail, peel and grate your <strong>carrots </strong>and roughly chop your <strong>roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and <strong>chopped roasted peanuts </strong>to the <strong>quick-pickled shallot</strong> and mix to combine – this is your <strong>quick-pickled Asian-style slaw</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>and <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a small bowl<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
