    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated hake</strong>,<strong> </strong>reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 2 min on each side or until cooked through and lightly crisp – this is your<strong> Thai-style hake</strong></p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
